{"tid":1720501,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"11月15日「查警暴 止警謊」銀髮族遊行已獲發「不反對通知書」","createTime":"2019-11-14T11:17:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T09:10:45.000Z","uid":240362,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5638266f8dfd78ce76953fc210aee88f8f8b7269","tid":1720501,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:17:35.000Z","msg":"**已獲發「不反對通知書」<br />\n**聽日大家著黑衫，配戴黑絲帶或者自行製作標語。<br />\n<br />\n「查警暴 止警謊」銀髮族遊行<br />\n<br />\n從反送中運動開始，政府屢誤戎機，每次都不能掌握最佳時刻去解決問題，反而令到局勢越演越烈！銀髪族曾多次提醒政府要好好地處理問題，但政府卻忠言逆耳，卒令香港社會發展到如斯境地！<br />\n<br />\n正所謂不賢者在高位，播其惡於衆也。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭不單解決不了問題！反而催生另一個更嚴重嘅警暴問題，又縱容警方每日都發放謊言！亦即是說暴力和謊言是香港政府賴以生存的手段！<br />\n<br />\n權力令人腐化、絕對權力令人絕對腐化。這點正正是近月來香港警察魔化的因由！<br />\n<br />\n作為市民我哋可以做啲乜嘢呢？<br />\n<br />\n短期應對方法包括不合作運動、罷工罷課罷市，迫使政府認真面對市民嘅訴求。<br />\n長遠應對嘅方法係改變現時嘅政制，香港市民需要真普選！我哋需要一個向市民負責嘅政府！我哋需要一個權力受到制衡嘅政府！我哋需要一個能夠保護市民嘅警隊，而唔係一個維穩嘅工具！<br />\n<br />\n香港每一個市民都應該竭盡全力去爭取一個真正為民嘅政府、更加應該為自己同埋下一代爭取一個有民主、自由、人權與及法治嘅香港！<br />\n<br />\n11月15日 星期五<br />\n下午4點：遮打花園集會<br />\n下午5點：由遮打起行<br />\n終點：公民廣場<br />\n<br />\n#1115集會遊行<br />\n#查警暴止警謊<br />\n#五大訴求<br />\n#缺一不可<br />\n#光復香港<br />\n#時代革命<br />\n<br />\n原文：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/845348632510629/posts/936543930057765?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F845348632510629%2Fposts%2F936543930057765%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=kXTsEwo%2F%2B0BMNdh3S%2FGVc%2FtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=62eab94b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/845348632510629/posts/936543930057765?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"6faaf73c61fc9842d2e3cbbd4c5ccf9e54834160","tid":1720501,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e5124f3ef0e47caafa0829259216fd41d5af7a","tid":1720501,"uid":50437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"335c061b68f7b380052a97b14999c5d7b2da295b","tid":1720501,"uid":50437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea241fd978d91df12ce1586fdfb362b98f599e0f","tid":1720501,"uid":50437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:18:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c08b990bdd29369b6620451d3f348488126448c","tid":1720501,"uid":50437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9f2e929b66f0934ae5fde1a3382cfb0d297381","tid":1720501,"uid":50437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:19:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/su